00:01:00.527 --> 00:01:02.535
Well seven doesn't
change with respect to x.

00:01:02.535 --> 00:01:03.504
The derivative of a constant,

00:01:03.504 --> 00:01:06.026
we've seen this multiple
times, is just zero.

00:01:06.026 --> 00:01:08.268
So it's just plus zero.

00:01:08.268 --> 00:01:10.285
