00:02:10.701 --> 00:02:11.784
And so, what is this?

00:02:11.784 --> 00:02:14.919
16 to the 1/4th is two,

00:02:14.919 --> 00:02:16.533
and then you cube two.

00:02:16.533 --> 00:02:19.439
Two to the third power is
eight, so that's eight.

00:02:19.439 --> 00:02:22.144
